              (156,156,1,   'Implementation of Peruvian Air Quality Law in the La Oroya Region', '<p> <ol> <li>{DOC Limpiar_el_Aire-2006.pdf March 2006 Draft: <i><b>Action Plan to Improve Air Qualtiy and Health in La Oroya</b></i> written by La Oroya Multisectoral Air-quality Board (<b>Spanish only</b>)} <li>{DOC Comentarios_de_AIDA-Limpiar_el_Aire.pdf AIDA Comments on the draft "Action Plan to Improve Air Qualtiy and Health in La Oroya" 06-03-31 (<b>Spanish only</b>)} </p> <p></ol></p> ','', '', NOW(), 1),
